parsed_data.ProjectTypes: Data migration, ETL pipeline development, Cloud infrastructure optimization
parsed_data.Summary: Goutham Aditya Pelluri is a results-driven Data Engineer with over 3 years of experience in designing and developing scalable data pipelines and cloud-based solutions. Proficient in Python and SQL, he has successfully implemented ETL workflows and optimized data processing efficiency using Azure Data Factory and Databricks. With a strong foundation in data modeling and big data frameworks, Goutham has a proven track record of delivering high-availability solutions and enhancing data accessibility for enterprise applications. His expertise in monitoring and troubleshooting, combined with a solid educational background in Computer Science, positions him as a valuable asset for organizations looking to leverage data for strategic decision-making.
